@startuml
title Sequence Diagram - Lihat History Data Sensor

actor "User" as User
participant "Halaman History" as Form
participant "Sistem" as System
participant "Database (SQLite)" as DB

' === Awal ===
User -> Form : Membuka halaman history
activate Form
Form -> User : Menampilkan tampilan awal (kosong)
deactivate Form

' === Permintaan data ===
Form -> System : Meminta data history sensor
activate System

System -> DB : Mengambil data dari SQLite
activate DB
DB -> DB : Eksekusi query SELECT
DB --> System : Mengirim data hasil query
deactivate DB

' === Tampilkan data ke user ===
System -> Form : Mengirim data history
activate Form
Form -> User : Menampilkan tabel / grafik data sensor
deactivate Form

' === User aksi tambahan (opsional) ===
User -> Form : Memilih filter atau rentang tanggal
activate Form
Form -> System : Meminta data baru berdasarkan filter
activate System
System -> DB : Query data sesuai filter
activate DB
DB --> System : Hasil filter dikirim
deactivate DB
System -> Form : Menampilkan hasil filter
activate Form
Form -> User : Menampilkan data terbaru
deactivate Form
deactivate System

' === Akhiran ===
User -> Form : Keluar dari halaman history
Form -> System : Menutup koneksi ke database
deactivate Form
deactivate System

@enduml
